init_text: Your entire life, you've been told you're deathly allergic to bees. You've always had people protecting you from them, be it your mother or a hired hand. Today, one slips through and lands on your shoulder. You hear a tiny voice say "Your Majesty, what are your orders?"

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The bee replied "You are the queen of the bees, the bees have chosen you to rule over them.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The bee then said "Your first order is to go to the meadow and make a hive."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I got a stick and a leaf and I made a little house.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I heard the bee say "It's very nice, but you forgot the most important thing."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "No, you are the queen and they will do anything for you," the bee replied.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Can you make me not allergic to bee stings?"
